<section>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>I am currently pursuing my Master of Science in Mathematics and Computing. My research interest is primarily Functional Analysis with Linear Algebra and Real Analysis. Alongwith mathematics, I use python and other computing tools like sagemath. I am interested in doing research with other mathemaaticians and find new ideas in the near future. My goal is to contribute to the mathematical community and collaborate with other similar minded people .</p>
</section>

